title: Deva

title: Bharat
subTitle: During the independent nation of India, a family gets torn apart, leaving an eight-year-old boy who makes a promise to his father to keep the family together.

subTitle: Shiva is a carefree lad who helps couples in love marry. Soon, he finds his own heart stolen, while being pursued by enemies determined to break them apart.

title: Dabangg
subTitle: Chulbul Pandey, a police officer, battles a corrupt political leader, Cheddi Singh, who strains Chulbul's relationship with his step-brother.

title: Dabangg

subTitle: An army intelligence officer arrives in Mumbai to spend the holiday with his family. However, he must switch back to work mode after a bomb rips through the heart of the city.

title: Kick

title: Maya Puthagum
subTitle: Guru, an assistant director, dreams of a dragon, which leads him to a mysterious book and its owner. The latter instructs him to meet a producer at a palace to film the manuscript's contents.
